#: app/templates/landing.html:583
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "Menene wannan?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:585
msgid ""
"The Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) helps teams add local knowledge to "
"map features by coordinating mapping in the field."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) yana taimaka wa ƙungiyoyi su ƙara ilimin"
" gari zuwa siffofin taswira ta hanyar daidaita aikin taswira a fili."

#: app/templates/landing.html:588
msgid ""
"Field-TM facilitates collaborative mapping by supporting and extending "
"mature tools like ODK and QField. It is a standalone mobile and web "
"workflow that helps teams collect geospatial data efficiently with "
"commonly available Android devices."
msgstr ""
"Field-TM yana sauƙaƙa aikin taswira na haɗin gwiwa ta hanyar tallafa da "
"faɗaɗa kayan aiki masu ƙarfi kamar ODK da QField. Tsarin aiki ne na wayar"
" hannu da yanar gizo wanda ke taimaka wa ƙungiyoyi tattara bayanan sarari"
" cikin inganci ta amfani da na'urorin Android da ake yawan samu."

#: app/templates/landing.html:593
msgid "A project manager demonstrates FieldTM mapping workflow on a laptop"
msgstr ""
"Mai kula da aiki yana nuna tsarin aikin taswira na FieldTM a kan "
"kwamfutar tafi-da-gidanka"

#: app/templates/landing.html:599
msgid "Main Features"
msgstr "Muhimman siffofi"

#: app/templates/landing.html:602
msgid "Flexible Data Collection"
msgstr "Tattara bayanai mai sassauci"

#: app/templates/landing.html:604
msgid ""
"Support diverse survey forms, multiple data formats, and adaptable "
"workflows that fit different operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Yana tallafa wa fom ɗin bincike iri-iri, tsarin bayanai da yawa, da "
"tsarin aiki masu daidaituwa da suka dace da bukatun gudanarwa daban-"
"daban."

#: app/templates/landing.html:608
msgid "Open Source and Customizable"
msgstr "Buɗaɗɗen tushe kuma ana iya daidaitawa"

#: app/templates/landing.html:610
msgid ""
"Adapt Field-TM to your own survey logic, data structures, and integration"
" requirements."
msgstr ""
"Daidaita Field-TM da tsarin bincikeka, tsarin bayanai, da bukatun "
"haɗakawa."

#: app/templates/landing.html:614
msgid "Entity-Level Tracking"
msgstr "Bibiyar matakin abu"

#: app/templates/landing.html:616
msgid ""
"Monitor survey progress at task and feature level so managers can make "
"informed decisions quickly."
msgstr ""
"Sa ido kan ci gaban bincike a matakin aiki da siffa don masu kula su "
"yanke shawara cikin sauri da sani."

#: app/templates/landing.html:623
msgid "Who is it for?"
msgstr "Ga wa ne wannan?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:626
msgid "Project Manager"
msgstr "Mai kula da aiki"

#: app/templates/landing.html:627
msgid "Create and coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Ƙirƙira kuma daidaita kamfen na fili"

#: app/templates/landing.html:629
msgid ""
"Project managers use Field-TM to set up mapping projects, define areas of"
" interest, design survey forms, and split work into manageable tasks."
msgstr ""
"Masu kula da aiki suna amfani da Field-TM don kafa ayyukan taswira, "
"tantance yankunan sha'awa, ƙirƙirar fom ɗin bincike, da raba aiki zuwa "
"ayyuka masu sauƙin kulawa."

#: app/templates/landing.html:632
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
msgstr "Tantance yankin aiki sannan ka ɗora ko ka zaɓi fom na bincike"

#: app/templates/landing.html:633
msgid "Split the area into tasks and generate a data extract"
msgstr "Raba yankin zuwa ayyuka sannan ka samar da cire bayanai"

#: app/templates/landing.html:634
msgid "Publish the project to ODK Central or QFieldCloud"
msgstr "Wallafa aikin zuwa ODK Central ko QFieldCloud"

#: app/templates/landing.html:635
