"publishes a project, mappers access it directly in their mobile app of "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Masu taswira ba sa buƙatar shiga Field-TM. Da zarar mai kula da aiki ya "
"wallafa aiki, masu taswira za su iya shiga kai tsaye ta manhajar wayar da"
" suka zaɓa."

